== 製作 ==
2014年6月，[[沙恩·布萊克|沙恩·布萊克]]宣布將執導名為《The Nice Guys》的電影，由[[羅素·克洛|羅素·克洛]]和[[雷恩·葛斯林|雷恩·葛斯林]]主演以及[[喬·西佛|喬·西佛]]監製<ref>{{cite news|title=Ryan Gosling & Russell Crowe May Be 'Nice Guys' for Shane Black|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/ryan-gosling-russell-crowe-may-be-nice-guys-for-shane-black/|accessdate=2014-06-13|publisher=firstshowing.net|date=2014-06-12|archive-date=2014-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140617141750/http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/ryan-gosling-russell-crowe-may-be-nice-guys-for-shane-black/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]負責電影在北美的發行權<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros In ‘Nice Guys’ Talks With Shane Black, Russell Crowe, Ryan Gosling|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/warner-bros-in-nice-guys-talks-with-shane-black-russell-crowe-ryan-gosling/|publisher=deadline.com|accessdate=2016-05-21|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713012150/http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/warner-bros-in-nice-guys-talks-with-shane-black-russell-crowe-ryan-gosling/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月16日，[[瑪格麗特·庫利|瑪格麗特·庫利]]和[[安格瑞·萊絲|安格瑞·萊絲]]加入劇組<ref name=Rice-Qualley>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Ryan Gosling and Russell Crowe Thriller 'Nice Guys' Casts Female Leads|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ryan-gosling-russell-crowe-thriller-733267|accessdate=2014-09-17|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-09-16|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021355/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ryan-gosling-russell-crowe-thriller-733267|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月29日，宣布[[麥特·波莫|麥特·波莫]]參演電影<ref name=Bomer>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Matt Bomer Joins Ryan Gosling & Russell Crowe In ‘The Nice Guys’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/matt-bomer-ryan-gosling-russell-crowe-nice-guys-white-collar-843027/|accessdate=2014-10-01|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-09-29|archive-date=2014-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141002025126/http://deadline.com/2014/09/matt-bomer-ryan-gosling-russell-crowe-nice-guys-white-collar-843027/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月20日，[[凱斯·大衛|凱斯·大衛]]與[[博·納普|博·納普]]加入飾演一對殺手檔<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Ford|first2=Rebecca|title='Nice Guys' Casts Its Bad Guys|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/nice-guys-casts-bad-guys-739588?utm_source=twitter|accessdate=2014-10-21|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-10-20|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106064322/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/nice-guys-casts-bad-guys-739588?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月21日，宣布[[金·貝辛格|金·貝辛格]]將飾演首席法官<ref name=Basinger>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Ford|first2=Rebecca|title=Kim Basinger Joins Ryan Gosling, Russell Crowe in 'Nice Guys'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kim-basinger-joins-ryan-gosling-742671|accessdate=2014-10-22|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-10-21|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011027/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kim-basinger-joins-ryan-gosling-742671|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月7日，[[泰·辛普金斯|泰·辛普金斯]]將飾演名為巴比的角色<ref name=Simpkins>{{cite news|title=Ty Simpkins Joins ‘The Nice Guys’|url=http://deadline.com/2014/11/olivia-holt-same-kind-of-different-as-me-edmund-kingsley-capsule-1201276465/|accessdate=2014-11-10|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-11-07|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930201931/https://deadline.com/2014/11/olivia-holt-same-kind-of-different-as-me-edmund-kingsley-capsule-1201276465/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月13日，{{link-en|傑克·基墨|Jack Kilmer}}加入該片飾演艾蜜莉亞的朋友<ref name=KilmerCast>{{cite news|last1=Ford|first1=Rebecca|title='Palo Alto' Actor Jack Kilmer Joins 'Nice Guys'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/palo-alto-actor-jack-kilmer-748799|accessdate=2014-11-20|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-11-13|archive-date=2018-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620101232/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/palo-alto-actor-jack-kilmer-748799|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

正式拍攝於2014年10月27日在[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]和[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]的{{link-en|迪凱特 (喬治亞州)|Decatur, Georgia|迪凱特}}開始進行<ref>{{cite news|title=Ryan Gosling’s ‘The Nice Guys’ is Now Casting Actors for a Very Featured Role|url=http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/ryan-goslings-the-nice-guys-is-now-casting-actors-for-a-very-featured-role/|accessdate=2014-10-30|publisher=projectcasting.com|date=2014-10-05|archive-date=2014-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101210203/http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/ryan-goslings-the-nice-guys-is-now-casting-actors-for-a-very-featured-role/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月31日，劇組於亞特蘭大拍攝警局的場景<ref>{{cite news|title=Ryan Gosling’s ‘The Nice Guys’ Casting Call for a Police Station Scene|url=http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/ryan-goslings-the-nice-guys-casting-call-for-a-police-station-scene/|accessdate=2014-11-01|publisher=projectcasting.com|date=2014-10-28|archive-date=2014-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105211141/http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/ryan-goslings-the-nice-guys-casting-call-for-a-police-station-scene/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拍攝也在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]進行。

