電影原定2016年6月17日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|title=Russell Crowe-Ryan Gosling Pic ‘The Nice Guys’ Gets Summer 2016 Release Date|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/nice-guys-russell-crowe-ryan-gosling-release-date-shane-black-827715/|publisher=deadline.com|accessdate=2016-04-26|archive-date=2014-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905003714/http://deadline.com/2014/09/nice-guys-russell-crowe-ryan-gosling-release-date-shane-black-827715/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]將日期改為2016年5月20日，而原本的日期則排給《[[中央情爆員|中央情爆員]]》<ref>{{cite news|last1=Patten|first1=Dominic|title=Warner Bros Moves Up ‘The Nice Guys’ For Comedy ‘Central Intelligence’|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/the-nice-guys-central-intelligence-release-dates-warner-bros-dwanye-johnson-ryan-gosling-finding-dory-1201395236/|accessdate=2015-03-23|publisher=deadline.com|date=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019160421/https://deadline.com/2015/03/the-nice-guys-central-intelligence-release-dates-warner-bros-dwanye-johnson-ryan-gosling-finding-dory-1201395236/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《假會徵信社》獲得了一致好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據249位專業影評人持有92%的新鮮度，平均得分7.5/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_nice_guys/?search=Nice%20guys |title=The Nice Guys (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-05-15 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020160932/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_nice_guys/?search=Nice%20guys |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得分70，代表電影「普遍好評」<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-nice-guys |title=The Nice Guys reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-05-15 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117005446/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-nice-guys |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上則得到了7.4分。

據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，在A+至F之間觀眾給的評價約落在「B-」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/angry-birds-neighbors-2-the-nice-guys-weekend-box-office-1201760146/ |title='Angry Birds’ Is The Word With $42M-$44M No. 1 Opening; ‘Neighbors 2’ Lower With $25M – Box Office |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-24 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6hjcwXJaj?url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/angry-birds-neighbors-2-the-nice-guys-weekend-box-office-1201760146/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|Uproxx|Uproxx}}的邁克·萊恩<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uproxx.com/movies/the-nice-guys-review/ |title=‘The Nice Guys’ Is A Blast To The Past (And Also Just A Blast) |website=Uproxx |accessdate=2016-05-15 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024082632/https://uproxx.com/movies/the-nice-guys-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[IGN|IGN]]都分別給了電影正面的評價，其中[[IGN|IGN]]給了本片9／10的高分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ie.ign.com/articles/2016/05/15/the-nice-guys-review |title=The Nice GuysReview |website=IGN |accessdate=2016-05-15}}</ref>；兩者都一致認為其劇本、演員和[[沙恩·布萊克|沙恩·布萊克]]的黑色幽默風格讓電影緊張又有趣。

=== 票房 ===
電影在北美於2016年5月20日上映，與《[[惡鄰纏身2|惡鄰纏身2]]》和《[[憤怒鳥玩電影|憤怒鳥玩電影]]》一同上映，預計能在首映週末獲得1000萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/captain-america-civil-war-opening-weekend-box-office-summer-records-1201750394/|title=Why ‘Captain America: Civil War’ Is Poised To Be This Summer’s Top-Grossing Live-Action Film: B.O. Postmortem|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-05-09|accessdate=2016-05-10|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6hOTbBBsj?url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/captain-america-civil-war-opening-weekend-box-office-summer-records-1201750394/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在週四晚上獲得了70萬美元的票房<ref name="Thursday">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/angry-birds-neighbors-2-the-nice-guys-weekend-box-office-1201760146/ |title=‘Neighbors 2’ Parties Harder Than ‘Angry Birds’ Thursday Night – Box Office |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-24 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6hjcwXJaj?url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/angry-birds-neighbors-2-the-nice-guys-weekend-box-office-1201760146/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首週末票房收入為1130萬美元位居當週第四，排於《[[憤怒鳥玩電影|憤怒鳥玩電影]]》（3900萬美元）、《[[美國隊長3：英雄內戰|美國隊長3：英雄內戰]]》（3310萬美元）和《[[惡鄰纏身2|惡鄰纏身2]]》（2180萬美元）之後<ref name=CinemaScore/>。

